{
  "name": "media-stack",
  "description": "Self-hosted, Docker Compose-based streaming media platform for sharing home apps (Jellyfin, Immich, the *arr stack, Matrix, and more) with family and friends. Pangolin reverse-proxy plus Keycloak provide unified SSO, social login, and automated TLS so users get a single branded login across services without installing a VPN; each top-level directory is an independent compose project orchestrated by a top-level Makefile.",
